{"id": "1434198255951937566", "channel_id": "1357183866183618741", "type": 0, "author_id": "734052554027040809", "author_name": "quan8122", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@153999495347044352>  Hi flares, these are my chars. Could you help me create 5 teams from the list (+1 borrowing) so that I can pass stage 2 or 3 in the D-effect zone?   I would be extremely appreciated of your help.", "timestamp": "2025-11-01T15:11:50.334000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["153999495347044352"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1434198255260012756", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-11-01-22-02-20-377_com.qookkagames.z1.qooapp.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 202335, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1357183866183618741/1434198255260012756/Screenshot_2025-11-01-22-02-20-377_com.qookkagames.z1.qooapp.jpg?ex=69cd35b6&is=69cbe436&hm=33954c7ebdd6362ae6603503b5c5b3d255a949aac9a43efa79edc32dd646fe85&"}, {"id": "1434198255696089170", "filename": "Screenshot_2025-11-01-22-02-14-038_com.qookkagames.z1.qooapp.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 214020, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1357183866183618741/1434198255696089170/Screenshot_2025-11-01-22-02-14-038_com.qookkagames.z1.qooapp.jpg?ex=69cd35b6&is=69cbe436&hm=1ebf26f1801a29a5e48c74e100111ad0d34c62f9816c1a74f855d062a1c54cf0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1357183866183618741", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Flares' Comprehensive Beginner Guide to Morimens", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704"]}
