{"id": "1434209250988654685", "channel_id": "1434209250988654685", "type": 0, "author_id": "1326453311314071594", "author_name": "authorigas", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi all! Looking to start Morimens today, hoping I'll be able to get some basic beginner advice. Aside from the usual \"Who should I pull on beginner banner\" (I was advised Caceus) And \"Should I pull on the current limited banner?\" (Consensus seems to be wait for the anniversary banner.) \n\nI'm hoping to know what I should focus on at the start of the game. Story progression? What should I be farming? How do I best avoid \"wasting\" my early game  resources? Andy advice would be greatly appreciated!", "timestamp": "2025-11-01T15:55:31.755000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1434209250988654685", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "What to focus on at the start?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747333490184292"]}
{"id": "1434245871251357696", "channel_id": "1434209250988654685", "type": 0, "author_id": "756552645661032682", "author_name": "enternameunavailable", "author_bot": false, "content": "Caecus is good, still usable in late game. But otherwise no real standard is far from reach, and 1 copy isn't game changing difference.\n\nLimited banner? Castor, even at e0 excellent shield/tank for your team. At e3 he becomes your DPS.\n\nJust farm event and do your weeklies. There's no real wasting, the biggest things you could possible waste are timeloop copy and Prototype Horizon those only come by once a month in shop and you use them for your limited units you really like and wheels.\n\nStory progression go on your own paste. Chapter 1-5 is comfortably human translated but not proofread. I did entirety of arc 1 and some events in 1 month", "timestamp": "2025-11-01T18:21:02.706000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1434209250988654685", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "What to focus on at the start?", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747333490184292"]}
{"id": "1434113854845095966", "channel_id": "1434113854845095966", "type": 0, "author_id": "895596580290297867", "author_name": "tev8_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "im currently using this and im struggling on chap 5 boss, im probably just underleveled but js wondering if i can make any better teams", "timestamp": "2025-11-01T09:36:27.542000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1434113855285624832", "filename": "IMG_0442.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 594696, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1434113854845095966/1434113855285624832/IMG_0442.png?ex=69cce71b&is=69cb959b&hm=87fabd3311fecbf807c038d8bee9ca23847df63fa17c36a7d13ca83f0f69e8b9&"}, {"id": "1434113855579095070", "filename": "IMG_0443.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 675104, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1434113854845095966/1434113855579095070/IMG_0443.png?ex=69cce71b&is=69cb959b&hm=e329f404044c2a3751feab570bfe9b2ed8eab8747f6c32f8384c341623a123c1&"}, {"id": "1434113855939940392", "filename": "IMG_0444.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 682792, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1434113854845095966/1434113855939940392/IMG_0444.png?ex=69cce71b&is=69cb959b&hm=135a83d2d0efc7c9c15a13f47548fcc0894291fcc26c2bb794af92364a51d699&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1434113854845095966", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "team building", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747489132412979", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1434130943400087622", "channel_id": "1434113854845095966", "type": 0, "author_id": "513647413584592896", "author_name": "methanehydrate", "author_bot": false, "content": "Your team is fine. You just need to level up your skills and use R wheels (especially the one that lets you buy cursed relic in shop) instead of SR since you're still in arc 1.", "timestamp": "2025-11-01T10:44:21.771000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1434113854845095966", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "team building", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747489132412979", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1434134868979220480", "channel_id": "1434113854845095966", "type": 0, "author_id": "756552645661032682", "author_name": "enternameunavailable", "author_bot": false, "content": "The R wheels their talking about \n\nGreed\nFrenzy\nEmerge\n\nGluttony if you want extra hp.\nYou can replace heart, Incalc, and everything Nautila and Caecus are equipped with. \n\nUpgraded Tawil's pinion. Exalt.\n\nWhenever you exalt grab Vortex, Abyss Order and Lightning Strike. You can wait until she spawns Hydra's to use them, you can wait a bit for them to get lower in cost before using but that's up to you<:cute1:1356053053568192717> \n\nCursed Relics you want \nTrickerster Hat\nMind Engraving \nBlack Meteorite (preferably delete Ramona Defense card, or Nautila and Caecus Strike cards)\nCaecus Exalt for burst turn.\nAnd keeps spamming Tawil exalt to keep grabbing aoe cards", "timestamp": "2025-11-01T10:59:57.702000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1434113854845095966", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "team building", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747489132412979", "1400747088995811358"]}
